WEBVTT

00:08.279 --> 00:10.179
Some American management consultants...

00:10.285 --> 00:13.316
...recommend having meetings standing up to save time,...

00:18.612 --> 00:20.828
...which wouldn't suit this Japanese chairman,...

00:20.954 --> 00:24.371
...who likes to take the time to contemplate what is being discussed.

00:29.040 --> 00:32.323
It's fine to get some shut-eye in Thailand, but not like this.

00:32.599 --> 00:35.645
Showing the soles of your feet is one of the rudest things you can do.

00:36.060 --> 00:40.995
And this hand gesture in parts of Greece would also be frowned upon.

00:44.359 --> 00:48.063
At HSBC, we never underestimate the importance of local knowledge,...

00:48.319 --> 00:50.127
...particularly when it comes to your money...

00:50.435 --> 00:51.986
...because what we learned in one country...

00:52.147 --> 00:55.069
...can directly benefit our customers in another.

00:55.346 --> 00:58.516
HSBC, the world's local bank.

